'''施卢赫人'''<ref name="baike">{{cite encyclopedia |editor=中国大百科全书出版社汇编 |year=1998 |encyclopedia=[[中国大百科全书|中国大百科全书]] |edition=1 |series=民族 |publisher=中国大百科全书出版社 |location=北京 |page=53 }}</ref>（[[施卢赫语|施卢赫语]]：ⵉⵛⵍⵃⵉⵢⵏ ''ishelhien''；{{lang-fr|Chleuh}}<ref>{{cite book|last1=Dalby|first1=Andrew|title=Dictionary of Languages: The definitive reference to more than 400 languages|date=2015|publisher=Bloomsbury Publishing|isbn=978-1408102145|page=614|url=https://www.google.com/books?id=7dHNCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA614#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate=2 November 2016}}</ref>）又称'''希尔哈人'''（{{lang-en|Shilha people}}），[[北非|北非]]民族，主要居住于[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]的[[小阿特拉斯山脉|小阿特拉斯山脉]]、[[高阿特拉斯山脉|高阿特拉斯山脉]]、[[苏斯|苏斯地区]]和南部沿海地区<ref name=wwshilha>{{cite book|author=Wolfgang Weissleder|title=The Nomadic Alternative: Modes and Models of Interaction in the African-Asian Deserts and Steppes|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JRyqfpi5BKcC|year=1978|publisher=Walter de Gruyter|isbn=978-3-11-081023-3|pages=11–12|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211073843/https://books.google.com/books?id=JRyqfpi5BKcC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>''[[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]]'' 2008, [http://www.britannica.com/eb/topic-541262/Shluh Shluh] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/eb/topic-541262/Shluh |date=20080519214354 }}.</ref>，是摩洛哥主要的[[柏柏尔人|柏柏尔民族]]之一<ref name="Appiah2010shp">{{cite book|author=Marian Aguiar|editor=Anthony Appiah and Henry Louis Gates|title=Encyclopedia of Africa|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=A0XNvklcqbwC|year=2010|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-533770-9|page=175|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323150730/https://books.google.com/books?id=A0XNvklcqbwC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=James Stuart Olson|title=The Peoples of Africa: An Ethnohistorical Dictionary|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MdaAdBC-_S4C|year=1996|publisher=Greenwood|isbn=978-0-313-27918-8|page=91|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205080650/https://books.google.com/books?id=MdaAdBC-_S4C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Appiah2010shp2">{{cite book|author=Marian Aguiar|editor=Anthony Appiah and Henry Louis Gates|title=Encyclopedia of Africa|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=A0XNvklcqbwC|year=2010|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-533770-9|pages=106–107|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323150730/https://books.google.com/books?id=A0XNvklcqbwC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿拉伯人有时以施卢赫人（{{lang|ar|شلوح}}）代指全体柏柏尔人<ref name="Shoup2011p54">{{cite book|author=John A. Shoup|title=Ethnic Groups of Africa and the Middle East: An Encyclopedia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SPBfnT_E1mgC|year=2011|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-1-59884-362-0|pages=53–54|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724221122/https://books.google.com/books?id=SPBfnT_E1mgC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。施卢赫人传统上从事农业和畜牧业<ref>{{cite book|author=James Stuart Olson|title=The Peoples of Africa: An Ethnohistorical Dictionary|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MdaAdBC-_S4C|year=1996|publisher=Greenwood|isbn=978-0-313-27918-8|page=523|access-date=2021-01-24|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205080650/https://books.google.com/books?id=MdaAdBC-_S4C|dead-url=no}}</ref>，部分人过半游牧生活，在有水源的情况下种植作物，旱季则随牧群迁移<ref name=wwshilha/>。在一些特殊时期如战时，不同部落会互相合作，开放领地放牧权。这种合作关系后来体现为举行年度聚会的形式<ref>{{cite book|author=George Peter Murdock|title=Culture and Society: Twenty-Four Essays|url=https://archive.org/details/culturesocietytw00murd|date=15 October 1965|publisher=University of Pittsburgh Press|isbn=978-0-8229-7406-2|pages=[https://archive.org/details/culturesocietytw00murd/page/343 343]–344}}</ref>。

